snippet.title: Peder B. Helland
snippet.description:
Welcome! My name is Peder B. Helland and I am a Norwegian composer.

This is my official artist channel on YouTube. On this channel I share all of my work across different genres. If you're only interested in my relaxing music, I recommend subscribing to Soothing Relaxation as well. 

See you around and thank you so much for listening to my music!
